Dianetics: The Modern Science of Mental Health
----------------------------------------------

It's a book which Scientology sells to raise a small amount of extra cash, it's sold to the more intelligent as a way to make money without being seen as a form of con.

This book is full of both intelligent and stupid topics, enjoy it.  It's all provided freely courtesy of anonymous individuals, this torrent is intended to help share the free knowledge.
